web-recap (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix shorthand flag `-z` not working for dump `--compress`.
  * Fix MongoDB ingestion counting bug that double-counted updated records in bulk write mode.
  * Remove confusing `keep` alias from ingestion conflict strategy list and enforce validation.

